descript.abstract: This line shapefile represents California's offshore islands. This layer is part of a collection of data created by the California Department of Fish & Wildlife.
descript.purpose: These data are intended for researchers, students, policy makers, and the general public for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production.
descript.supplinf: Accuracy appears good by informal look at the vector over 1999 NOAA charts, however it has not been quantified.
